eoffset_demo.ini

Usage:
  1) Estop OFF  (F1)
  2) Machine ON (F2)
  3) HOME All   (Ctrl-Home)
  4) Test external offset functionality
     using the sim_pin gui to alter the
     per-axis hal pins:

     axis.*.eoffset-scale
     e:<*>counts => axis.*.eoffset-counts)

  5) Soft limit trespass is detected by
     hal logic and stops the machine.
     To restart:
       a) Estop OFF  (F1)
       b) Machine ON (F2)
       d) jog from offending soft limit

Automatic stopping for soft limit violations
may be disabled with sim_pin toggle of:
  e:override_limit_stop
